# ğŸ”„ PC â†”ï¸ Phone File Sync via Wi-Fi

A minimal Python-based system to **monitor files on your PC** and **sync them automatically to your Android phone** over a local Wi-Fi network using a Flask API server.

> ğŸš« No cloud. No cables. Just fast, local sync.

---

## ğŸ“¦ Features

- âœ… Auto-detect new and modified files
- âœ… Sync to phone over HTTP
- âœ… Create missing folders remotely
- âœ… Simple setup using Python only
- âœ… Keeps everything locally in your phone

